7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Fireflies.ai and Morgen share a solid foundation of core features including Task Management, Ai Assistant, Calendar, Integrations. Where Fireflies.ai pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Notes and Collaboration and Automation and Analytics, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Fireflies.ai holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Morgen scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Fireflies.ai and Morgen offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Fireflies.ai's free tier and Morgen's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
