b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Fireflies.ai is best suited for sales teams, recruiters, remote teams, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Morgen, meanwhile, shines for multi calendar users, freelancers, remote workers, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2016, Fireflies.ai describes itself as \"AI meeting assistant that records, transcribes, and summarizes conversations.\" Morgen, established in 2020, positions itself as \"Unified calendar app with task integration and intelligent scheduling across platforms.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Fireflies.ai** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to more features (9 vs 5), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Morgen is a poor choice — far from it. Morgen excels in its own right, particularly for multi calendar users and freelancers.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value works across all major meeting platforms, go with Fireflies.ai. If works with google, outlook, and icloud matters more to you, Morgen is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
